---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Container from '../../components/ui/Container.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for MAKO Consult website. Information about data collection, processing, and your rights under GDPR."
  lang="en"
  canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
  <section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <Container>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-3xl">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

        <h2>1. Overview</h2>
        <p>This privacy policy explains how MAKO Consult ("we", "us") collects, uses, and protects your personal data when you visit our website.</p>

        <h2>2. Controller</h2>
        <p>
          Michael Makowiecki<br />
          MAKO Consult<br />
          Bundesweg 1<br />
          20146 Hamburg, Germany<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:info@makoconsult.de">info@makoconsult.de</a>
        </p>

        <h2>3. Data Collection on This Website</h2>

        <h3>Hosting</h3>
        <p>Our website is hosted as a static site. The hosting provider may collect server log files (IP address, browser type, access time). This data is processed based on Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in secure operation).</p>

        <h3>Contact Form</h3>
        <p>When you use our contact form, the data you provide (name, email, message) is transmitted to Formspree, Inc. for processing. This is based on Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR (pre-contractual measures). Your data is used only to respond to your inquiry.</p>

        <h3>Cal.com</h3>
        <p>We use Cal.com for appointment scheduling. When you book a call, Cal.com processes your data according to their privacy policy (cal.com/privacy). This is based on Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR.</p>


        <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your personal data (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
          <li>Rectification of inaccurate data (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
          <li>Erasure of your data (Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
          <li>Restriction of processing (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
          <li>Data portability (Art. 20 GDPR)</li>
          <li>Object to processing (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise these rights, please contact us at the email address above.</p>

        <h2>5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The current version is always available on this page.</p>

        <p class="text-sm text-steel">Last updated: March 2026</p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
